&lt;p&gt;County Durham and Darlington NHS Foundation Trust is one of the largest integrated care providers in England, serving a population of around 600,000 people. We are a high performing organisation with a track record of success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity to work within the busy hyper acute stroke unit at University Hospital of North Durham. We deliver high standards of stroke care to County Durham and Darlington. The post holder will support, and be a part of the professional multidisciplinary team in contributing to a high standard of stroke care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A commitment to providing and adhering to high standards of nursing care is an essential requirement for this post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is your chance to be involved with an amazing team!&lt;/p&gt;
